### Transfer Service HTTP Requests
### Usage: In IntelliJ IDEA or any HTTP client that supports .http files, place cursor on a request and run it.

@host = localhost
@port = 8085
@baseUrl = http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/transfers

### Create a transfer (POST /api/transfers)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transferId": "{{$uuid}}",
  "fromAccount": "ACC-1234",
  "toAccount": "ACC-5678",
  "amount": 250.75,
  "transferDate": "{{$datetime iso8601}}",
  "status": "PENDING",
  "description": "Test transfer via HTTP file"
}

### Create and process a sample transfer (GET /api/transfers/sample)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sample

### Create and process a large sample transfer (GET /api/transfers/large-sample)
GET {{baseUrl}}/large-sample
